These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, raspberry, pepper, radish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, classical, trance, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, turkish, egyptian, australian
4 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, pony, turtle
 1. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 2. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4
 3. the dutch is on the left of the fan of trance##1
 4. the egyptian is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 6. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 7. the turkish is the person eating pepper##1
 8. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the turtle and the fan of pop##2
10. the person eating grapefruit is the owner of the turtle##1
11. the fan of trance is the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | pepper  | grapefruit    | radish    | raspberry   |
| Music-Genre   | classical     | soul   | trance       | pop    |
| Nationality   | turkish | dutch | australian    | egyptian |
| Pet           | dog | turtle       | ferret | pony     |

