.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, nectarine, spinach, cucumber
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, board-games, reading, dancing
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, thai, brazilian, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, golf, ice-hockey, skateboarding
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
 2. the thai is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 4. the person eating nectarine is the malaysian##1
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the malaysian is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 7. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 8. the russian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 9. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating spinach is in an odd position##4
11. the brazilian is the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | broccoli  | nectarine    | spinach     | cucumber       |
| Hobby         | reading | dancing | fishing   | board-games |
| Nationality   | brazilian | malaysian   | thai   | russian    |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | skateboarding  | rugby | golf   |

