.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, fanta, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, doctor, lawyer, security-guard
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, russian, thai, indian
4 different pets are kept: bird, rat, snake, ferret
 1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the teacher##3
 2. the russian is the lawyer##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 4. the teacher is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is the security-guard##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the indian##1
 8. the security-guard is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the spanish##1
10. the owner of the bird is the person drinking fanta##1
11. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | tea | fanta   | water    | almond-milk      |
| Job           | lawyer | teacher | doctor | security-guard     |
| Nationality   | russian      | indian   | spanish   | thai |
| Pet           | ferret         | bird       | snake  | rat       |

