.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, onion, grapes, cherry
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing, photography, gardening
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, lacrosse, rugby, biathlon
 1. the person drinking milk is the person eating pomegranate##1
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 8. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating cherry##1
12. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk       | hot-chocolate   | milk   | lemonade   |
| Food       | onion        | cherry | pomegranate    | grapes       |
| Hobby      | gardening | rock-climbing    | photography  | cooking |
| Sport      | lacrosse  | rugby  | swimming | biathlon    |

