.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, lime, pomegranate, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, singing, puzzles, card-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, nurse, freelancer, chef
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, lacrosse, water-polo, rowing
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person eating grapes##2
 3. the freelancer is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 4. the nurse is the person eating apple##1
 5. the security-guard is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating lime is the security-guard##1
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the nurse##1
 9. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
10. the nurse is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | pomegranate    | grapes      | apple          | lime    |
| Hobby   | singing | card-games       | puzzles | traveling |
| Job     | chef     | freelancer      | nurse     | security-guard |
| Sport   | lacrosse   | rowing | water-polo        | volleyball   |

