 3. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 4. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 5. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of electronic is between the american and the fan of house##2
 7. the fan of trance is the person eating blueberry##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating blueberry##1
 9. the argentine is on the far right##1
10. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
