The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, baseball, ice-hockey, parkour
 1. the person eating banana is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of pop is between the person watching thriller movies and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
 6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 7. the fan of electronic is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is parkour is the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person eating peach is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
11. the person eating peach is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
13. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
