.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, water, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, writing, dancing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, scientific, disaster, family
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, baseball, golf, lacrosse
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
11. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | water       | soy-milk | cola        | tea        |
| Hobby         | dancing | writing       | filmmaking | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | scientific        | adventure    | disaster      |
| Sport         | baseball     | golf    | lacrosse | rowing   |

