.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, jazz, funk, country
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, malaysian, mexican, italian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, soccer, climbing, weightlifting
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, trike, subway, taxi
 1. the fan of country is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is between the spanish and the italian##2
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the malaysian##1
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 6. the fan of jazz is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 7. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 8. the italian is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
10. the spanish is in an even position##4
11. the spanish is on the far right##1
12. the fan of disco is on the right of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | disco | country     | funk        |
| Nationality   | mexican | italian  | malaysian     | spanish |
| Sport         | soccer    | ice-hockey | climbing      | weightlifting |
| Transport     | taxi | trike     | subway | bus       |

 